<emphasis id="337698834F16EF5E633D43454538AEF1" italics="true" pageNumber="279">Bot. Commelins:</emphasis>
124. 1983) provided current names for each unnamed variety listed in the original description, as did Newton (in Eggli, 
<emphasis id="E039C38C6B04A59D7656A4E6B13F379E" italics="true" pageNumber="279">Ill. Handb. Succ. Pl., Monocots:</emphasis>
133. 2001). The latter appears to treat this name as synonymous with 
<taxonomicName id="8DDA0E090D874DA7AC5CDED7C3D942B9" authority="Mill." authorityName="Mill." class="Liliopsida" family="Xanthorrhoeaceae" genus="Aloe" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ferox">
